<h1>Quiz application</h1>

<p>This is an application where you can add and answer to existing questions for different topics. Anyone using the application can view the available topics, add questions to them, and answer to the existing ones.</p>

<p>If you haven't used the application before, you can start by <a href="/auth/register">registering</a>. If you have been here before, just <a href="/auth/login">log in</a>!</p>
